        {
            "title": "與日本爭執不下之際 中國向法國尋求支持",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 中國最高外交官王毅在與法國對口官員的通話中表示，雙方應當相互支持。這顯示在與日本爭執不下之際，北京努力爭取外交支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">王毅周四與法國總統的外交顧問埃馬紐埃爾·博納通話，說日本首相高市早苗本月早些時候「發表涉台挑釁言論」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據中國外交部發布的聲明，王毅表示，北京和巴黎應當「在涉及對方核心利益問題上堅定相互支持」，「希望法方繼續堅定恪守一個中國原則。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"王毅攝影：奧馬爾·哈瓦那/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AbTBjDgXC4fjVorS0Cls9A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c0848ea35e21b1cdd11d129f6329ad68\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">王毅攝影：奧馬爾·哈瓦那/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國駐北京大使館尚未回應周五上班前所發尋求評論的請求。法國總統埃馬紐埃爾·馬克龍下周即將對中國進行國事訪問，就經濟和商業事宜進行磋商。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-619334a5-9fd4-318c-8bd0-e40f1ca8d61e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中國因高市早苗涉及台灣的言論與日本陷入糾紛之際，中國正努力爭取外交支持，上周致函聯合國秘書長安東尼奧·古特雷斯，指責高市違反國際法，公然將台灣海峽危機與日本可能部署軍力聯繫起來。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市拒絕了中國讓她撤回11月7日所發表言論的要求。她當時說，如果在台灣衝突中使用武力，對日本而言可能構成「存亡危機事態」。這是日本在任首相首次發表此類言論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本首相高市早苗稱之前談及台灣問題時並未打算提及任何細節</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Turns to France for Support During Its Feud With Japan</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Colum Murphy、Alfred Liu.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
