        {
            "title": "美團出現2022年以來首次虧損 為價格戰付出代價",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HwbrCyqjfq4Q5JTu4yfTMA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/62ea91aca2a7545f1c40ecc3169edf40\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美團近三年來首次出現虧損，反映出在中國消費市場疲軟之際，它與<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿里巴巴;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿里巴巴\">阿里巴巴</a>、京東三方大戰的沉重代價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司公佈三季度淨虧損160億元人民幣（23億美元），超出分析師平均預計的140億元。營收成長至955億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一業績凸顯出，阿里巴巴和京東雙雙投入數十億元用於打折和補貼，以進一步耕耘外賣市場，給美團造成壓力。美團被迫迎戰，採取了同類措施，導致成長放緩之際利潤率也告下降。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X0AX_F9ThqvmTXI.a7DKaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/12733a5d0390dd95e7825abc8947f8ff\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Meituan Records First Loss Since 2022 After Price War Takes Toll</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3347f438-e58d-3c4e-aef9-9d9b69d4120b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE2022%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D-%E7%82%BA%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%88%B0%E4%BB%98%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%A3%E5%83%B9-090250968.html",
