        {
            "title": "萬科境內債場內外價格「冰火兩重天」 令交易員百思不得其解",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"825\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/26kFVd7kImzmkIqOBT8LNw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1520cdbac3b17fd7c2579e267972e882\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 萬科境內債的劇烈波動連續第二天令信用交易員感到困惑，市場正在等待該開發商計畫將其下月到期的一筆境內債展期的細節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科周三晚間發布公告，尋求將12月15日到期的20億元人民幣債券展期。這一舉動令市場極為震驚，加劇對該公司潛在違約的擔憂。萬科部分美元債重挫，跌至紀錄新低，港股也大幅下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">境內債同樣大幅下跌，但盤中卻出現意外飆升，引起交易員密切關注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五開盤後不久，萬科「22萬科02」境內債最低跌至27元，較周四收盤價跌超30%，被深交所實施臨時停牌至15:27。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e85fb40d-e9de-372f-86b0-c458f3bfbd75-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編數據顯示，該債券在場內停牌約半小時後，在場外協商交易中大幅反彈，回升至88元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"825\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LsQWMTgcHpTS4yr171uJ2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5b19fb961f110b2e49cc4d7a2a13933f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科其他一些債券也出現類似交易模式，先是在交易所匹配成交的場內交易中大幅下跌至深度困境債水平，又在場外協商交易中成交價大幅反彈至90元左右。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據幾位境內債交易員稱，在場外協商交易中，買賣雙方可以自行協商並最終確定條款，為市場參與者提供了更大靈活性，但對公眾而言透明度較低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前尚不清楚這些交易員為何願以遠高於市場價的價格買入這些票據，理論上他們本可以以低於40元的價格買入。但在定價可能受到內幕消息扭曲的市場中，這種異常情況並不罕見。虛假交易也可用於在不同賬戶之間轉移高風險持倉，以最大限度地減少某些產品的損失，而較低的市場流動性則會放大價格波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科計畫於12月10日召開持有人會議，討論展期相關事項。其他細節尚未公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博匯編數據，萬科2027年和2029年到期的美元票據周五早盤延續跌勢，每1美元面值買價約在20美分。萬科港股周五上午一度上漲3.4%，周四時重挫7.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Builder China Vanke’s Yuan Bond Gyrations Confound Credit Market</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Emma Dong、Jin Wu.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%90%AC%E7%A7%91%E5%A2%83%E5%85%A7%E5%82%B5%E5%A0%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%96%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC-%E5%86%B0%E7%81%AB%E5%85%A9%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A9-%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E7%99%BE%E6%80%9D%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E8%A7%A3-073741078.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-28 16:05:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐盟主要經濟體物價走勢分化 法國通膨意外持穩而西班牙略超預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國11月通膨意外較上月持穩，西班牙通膨回落但降幅小於分析師預期，凸顯該地區主要經濟體的物價走勢出現分化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國的歐盟調和CPI同比增速穩定在0.8%，此前預測為小幅上升至1%。西班牙的歐盟調和CPI同比增速放緩至3.1%，此前彭博調查的預測中值為放緩至3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些數據是歐元四大經濟體今日密集發布的通膨數據的一部分，將為歐洲央行今年12月最後一次利率決策提供參考依據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">義大利的通膨率預計將維持在1.3%不變，而德國的通膨率預計將小幅上升至2.4%。歐元區將於12月2日公佈通膨數據，最終結果可能與10月的2.1%相去不遠，並接近歐洲央行2%的目標值。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a93b86c3-0ead-39e7-99ef-a9cf35751964-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">What Bloomberg Economics Says...</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“Euro-area inflation is likely to be unchanged in November before resuming a sustained deceleration in December. Those additional declines may increase pressure on the ECB to ease monetary policy again next year, although the Governing Council is resisting that move for the time being.”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—David Powell, senior euro-area economist. Click here for full PREVIEW</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題French Inflation Unexpectedly Holds Steady as Spain Stays Strong</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ainhoa Goyeneche、Joel Rinneby、Harumi Ichikura、Barbara Sladkowska.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%AB%94%E7%89%A9%E5%83%B9%E8%B5%B0%E5%8B%A2%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E6%8C%81%E7%A9%A9%E8%80%8C%E8%A5%BF%E7%8F%AD%E7%89%99%E7%95%A5%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-085732089.html",
